Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.player

Class Chamber

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.player.Chamber
All Implemented Interfaces:
StudentContainer, Serializable
public class Chamber extends Object implements Serializable, StudentContainer
The Chamber class models the chamber of the school board, with the students, professors and coins and the methods needed for their management
